name: Aussie Colonial Save the Date
description:
Julia Made is going into Wedding Stationary! I designed my own for my wedding and had very positive feed back. Now i can make your stationary using the unique and rustic look of the Gocco Printer... If you like this look then keep posted for my new upcoming range coming soon.

This Aussie Colonial style 'Save the Date' measures 105mm by 148mm, so imagine a general greeting card size or A5. I have used nice thick off white card stock of 160gsm, the finish is rustic and eco chic.

Each invite comes with a brown kraft envelope with hand printed address box. Please convo me with amount and i will send an invoice though and get to work making your beautiful 'Save the Dates'
